  		</div>
   </div>
   <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="mt-4 jb-header">About The Club</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="jumbotron mt-4 text-center">
      <p class="jb-txt">We are a group of pupils at the school who like poker but don't want to lose too much money. <br/>
      So, we have founded a club which hosts small buy-in tournament - but with all the official Texas Hold 'Em No Limits Rules.</p>
